	* gcc.target/powerpc/ppc-fpconv-3.c: Likewise.

	* gcc.target/powerpc/ppc-fpconv-8.c: Likewise.

	* gcc.target/powerpc/recip-4.c: Likewise.
	* gcc.target/powerpc/recip-5.c: Likewise.

From-SVN: r179876
